translations: n.涤纶（英国合成纤维之一，商标名）

phrs.translation: 涤纶, 特丽纶, 丽绫

sentences.sentence: The surface modification of air low-temperature plasma on Terylene fiber is observed.
sentences.translation: 观测了空气低温等离子体对涤纶纤维的表面改性作用。

sentences.sentence: This paper introduces the result of the research on the treatment of the terylene wastewater by UASB reactor.
sentences.translation: 报道了采用升流式厌氧污泥床(UASB)处理涤纶废水的试验结果。

sentences.sentence: A new method is introduced to make transparent plot films, in which a blotting layer is coated on terylene film base.
sentences.translation: 介绍了在涤纶片基上涂布吸墨层，制作透明绘图胶片的方法和使用该胶片进行专题图、地形图审校的工艺。
